{"tid":1789764,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"星火依單野係燃料","createTime":"2019-12-19T13:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T17:43:11.000Z","uid":130214,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"050b81506d812c2c23f1748acc133c6b2d494888","tid":1789764,"uid":130214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T13:43:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係重燃運動熱度既燃料！！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n知唔知點解最近咁多人被上門拘捕<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為冇大型行動！</span></span></strong><br />\n知唔知點解最近咁多人被自殺<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為冇大型行動！</span></span></strong><br />\n知唔知點解星火資金被凍結<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為冇大型行動！</span></span></strong><br />\n知唔知點解最近咁多人嬲完喇<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為冇大型行動！</span></span></strong><br />\n知唔知點解最近咁多人過返正常生活<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為冇大型行動！</span></span></strong><br />\n知唔知點解有好多被捕手足喊緊<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係因為冇大型行動！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇哂行動 黑警慳返部署時間去著手其他方面繼續降溫</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">知唔知仲有好多手足唔想後悔佢地既付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: green;\">手足們 唔好灰心 大家休息完喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>釋放義士唔係信念 係結果<br />\n今個聖誕大家可唔可以唔好掉底在囚